text: I Don't Think I Can Do This Anymore is the third studio album by British emo band Moose Blood. The album was released on 9 March 2018. It was followed by a tour of the UK and Northern America. ==Reception== I Don't Think I Can Do This Anymore received mixed to positive reviews from critics upon release.
